<B>__{chingachgook}
<A>__{has their weapons slung over his back. he says something in mohican. uncas spins looks at alice: her expression's vacant. hawkeye's knife cuts a lock of cora's hair. he folds it into his shirt. the orange light from huron torches, now closer, plays on the wall behind her. we hear many huron approach. chingachgook & uncas now run out of the cave and throw themselves into the curtain of water. this is their exit.}
<B>__{hawkeye}
